Technical description

The MQM Quantometer is a turbine wheel gas meter that registers the oper- ating volume using a 8-digit mechanical counter.

Dieser Text ist im Dokument: 293144_DB MQM Pressure gauge -GB- zu finden. Produktkategorie: Gaszähler, Produkt ID: 293144, Produktname: DB MQM Pressure gauge -GB-. The MQM is a volume flow meter. The flow of the measured gas causes the turbine wheel to rotate.

Via pulses the operating volume can be transferred to an electronic volume corrector and converted to normal or standard conditions.

Threaded connection

Rp 1 & Rp 1 ½, acc. ISO 7/1:

max. operating pressure 4 bar

Flanged connection

DN 25 to DN 150, acc. DIN EN 1092-1:

max. operating pressure 16 bar.

Application

Dieser Text ist im Dokument: 293144_DB MQM Pressure gauge -GB- zu finden. Produktkategorie: Gaszähler, Produkt ID: 293144, Produktname: DB MQM Pressure gauge -GB-. The MQM is for operational gas-volume measurement and is suitable for gases of families 1, 2, 3 and other neutral gaseous media. MQM is not an offical calibrated counter. It is used for internal controlling processes, most suitable for industrial thermoprocessing facilities.

Approvals

EU type testing certificate as per:

• EU-Pressure Equipment Directive
